---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Badge from "../components/Badge.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import HomelabStatus from "../components/HomelabStatus.astro";
---

<Layout title="WolfLink115">

<main>

<Navbar />

<div class="hero">

    <img src="/avatar.png" alt="WolfLink115" class="avatar" />

    <h1>Heya goobers, I'm WolfLink115! 🐺</h1>

    <p class="subtitle">
        Welcome to my little corner of the internet.
    </p>

</div>

<div class="badges">

<Badge color="#30363d" text="🐧 Linux Lover" />
<Badge color="#0969da" text="🐳 Docker Enjoyer" />
<Badge color="#6f42c1" text="☁ Homelab" />
<Badge color="#2ea043" text="💻 Surface Pro 6" />
<Badge color="#da3633" text="🔥 Breaking Things" />
<Badge color="#8250df" text="🐺 Am WOOF!!!" />

</div>

<HomelabStatus />

<p>
I'm mostly just a nerd who enjoys taking things apart to figure out how they work...
and occasionally putting them back together again.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>Things I have been messing with as of recent</h2>

<div class="grid">

<Card emoji="🐧" title="Linux">
Learning Linux has become one of my favorite hobbies.
</Card>

<Card emoji="🐳" title="Docker">
Running nearly everything in containers these days.
</Card>

<Card emoji="☁️" title="Self-hosting">
Building my own little corner of the internet.
</Card>

<Card emoji="📸" title="Immich">
My replacement for Google Photos.
</Card>

<Card emoji="🎬" title="Jellyfin">
Movies, TV shows, and music without subscriptions.
</Card>

<Card emoji="🔍" title="SearXNG">
Privacy-friendly search is awesome.
</Card>

</div>

<p>
Lately I've been building out my own homelab (running an entire server on this dingy
$95 Surface Pro 6 I bought off Marketplace lmao), trying to learn about porting UEFI
to old devices, etc.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>Current projects</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Building my homelab</li>
  <li>Random Linux experiments on old phones I have laying around lol</li>
  <li>Trying to find stability, privacy, and security in all that I do.</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h2>Hobbies?</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Playing games (though, not that many. VRChat, Beat Saber, and The Legend of Zelda are really the only games I enjoy playing)</li>
  <li>Tinkering with old devices.</li>
  <li>Being a fluffy woofer.</li>
  <li>Existing (does that count as a hobby?)</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h2>A singular fun fact about me</h2>

<p><strong>Am WOOF!!!</strong></p>

<hr>

<h2>Oh, and here is my website lol</h2>

<p>
🌐 <a href="https://www.wolflink115.com">www.wolflink115.com</a>
</p>

<p>
If one of my services isn't responding, there's a good chance my Surface is asleep,
powered off, or I'm busy breaking—I mean <em>improving</em>—something.
</p>

</main>
</Layout>
